app_description: Easy to use simple and powerful way to create great videos. Turn your best photos and videos into a professional composition in minutes! This video editing app comes with a wide range of editing tools to mix photos and videos to create professional video clips that you can share with family and friends. Combine photos and videos with ease Add stickers text GIFs and filters Built in music and audio effects Record in app live audio Create transitions between photos and videos Set a background color Choose aspect ratio Share with friends and family or save movies to your iPhone gallery Music and SFX by https: artlist.io Icons and some graphics thanks to flaticon.com and pexels.com
